RandomExtended - Class in com.swirlds.platform
A class similar to Random, but with extra methods to clone it and add entropy, and without thread safety.
RandomExtended() - Constructor for class com.swirlds.platform.RandomExtended
Initialize with a random seed, based on the current time.
RandomExtended(long) - Constructor for class com.swirlds.platform.RandomExtended
Initialize with the given seed, so all future numbers will be a purely deterministic function of the initial seed, the numbers passed to absorbEntropy, and when absorbEntropy is called in the sequence of generated numbers.
